&lt;h1 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior QA Engineer (AI-First | Full-Stack Quality)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
