&lt;h2 style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior QA Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; who thinks beyond traditional testing — someone who can&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;build quality systems&lt;/strong&gt;, not just validate them. This role is for an engineer who thrives in a &lt;strong&gt;fast-paced, dynamic environment&lt;/strong&gt;, embraces an &lt;strong&gt;AI-first approach&lt;/strong&gt;, and takes ownership of quality across the entire development lifecycle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
