&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opportunity:&lt;/strong&gt; Get Well is seeking a highly motivated Technical Product Owner to own the technical delivery of mobile experiences across iOS, Android, and PWAs on BYOD and clinical devices, including mobile Gen AI, security and MDM, and device hardware capabilities. In this role, you will shape innovative product strategies by owning technical delivery, backlog, sprint execution, and engineering coordination. You will closely collaborate with the US Senior PM of Patient and Family Experience to drive the roadmap while working cross-functionally with engineering and reporting into India product leadership / India PM. Your work will ensure that our mobile products continue to lead in innovation within the healthcare technology space.&lt;/p&gt;
